963
00:57:43,993 --> 00:57:45,085
We improvise.

964
00:57:45,160 --> 00:57:46,593
I've heard better plans, you know.

965
00:57:46,662 --> 00:57:47,959
Got another one?

966
00:57:48,030 --> 00:57:49,122
No.

967
00:57:49,198 --> 00:57:50,927
Then move it.

968
00:57:53,102 --> 00:57:54,126
Get down right now.

969
00:57:54,203 --> 00:57:55,795
We gotta see Taha.
It's mega-urgent.

970
00:57:55,871 --> 00:57:56,963
It is, huh?

971
00:57:57,039 --> 00:57:58,734
Well, for now you're going
to mega-get down...

972
00:57:58,807 --> 00:58:00,331
and mega-keep your mouth shut...

973
00:58:00,409 --> 00:58:01,467
got that?

974
00:58:01,543 --> 00:58:02,635
