975
00:58:02,711 --> 00:58:04,611
- What's your name again?
- What the fuck do you care?

976
00:58:04,680 --> 00:58:05,772
It's for Taha.

977
00:58:05,848 --> 00:58:06,940
When he asks whose fault it was...

978
00:58:07,016 --> 00:58:08,540
that he lost
twenty million Euros...

979
