985
00:58:20,162 --> 00:58:21,459
I wish I knew what we were doing.

986
00:58:21,530 --> 00:58:23,225
Stay loose
and just let it happen.

987
00:58:34,376 --> 00:58:35,308
Get ready to go.

988
00:58:35,377 --> 00:58:36,469
- Hey?
- Now!

989
00:59:02,404 --> 00:59:03,371
It's down there!

990
00:59:03,439 --> 00:59:05,407
That's the way out?
Through there? Great!

991
00:59:16,485 --> 00:59:18,316
Jesus!
You should have been a cop!

992
00:59:18,387 --> 00:59:19,581
- They'd have loved you!
