1236
01:18:42,577 --> 01:18:44,442
You sure you don't want
to stay on this side?

1237
01:18:44,513 --> 01:18:45,980
With the reward
you're going to get...

1238
01:18:46,047 --> 01:18:47,571
you could buy a real nice place.

1239
01:18:47,649 --> 01:18:49,116
I got a nice place.

1240
01:18:49,184 --> 01:18:50,674
Besides, this is where I live.

1241
01:18:50,752 --> 01:18:52,276
I was born here.

1242
01:18:52,354 --> 01:18:54,254
Now all I want to do
is live here in peace.

1243
01:18:54,322 --> 01:18:56,085
But you will, Leito.
They're going to be...

1244
01:18:56,158 --> 01:18:58,217
demolishing the wall
next week.

1245
01:18:58,293 --> 01:18:59,385
The police, the post office...

1246
01:18:59,461 --> 01:19:02,089
and the school
all open next month.

1247
01:19:02,164 --> 01:19:04,826
You know
it's down to you, all of that.

1248
01:19:04,900 --> 01:19:06,834
Older brother,
you're the greatest!

1249
01:19:06,902 --> 01:19:08,267
I've been saying that for years!

1250
01:19:08,336 --> 01:19:11,965
Come on, smile.
Lighten up.

1251
01:19:12,040 --> 01:19:13,667
I hope things don't get
messed up on the way...

1252
01:19:13,742 --> 01:19:14,970
and that they keep their promises.

1253
01:19:15,043 --> 01:19:16,101
Hey, these things aren't words.

1254
01:19:16,178 --> 01:19:17,805
They were voted on.

1255
01:19:17,879 --> 01:19:19,210
And government decrees
have to be applied.

1256
01:19:19,281 --> 01:19:20,373
It's the law.

1257
01:19:20,449 --> 01:19:21,814
And there's always
an asshole like me around...

1258
01:19:21,883 --> 01:19:23,373
to see that laws are obeyed.

1259
01:19:26,555 --> 01:19:27,544
Take care of yourself.

1260
01:19:27,622 --> 01:19:29,954
You make it sound as if
I live in the barrio like you.

1261
01:19:30,025 --> 01:19:32,516
Your neighborhood's
more dangerous than mine.

1262
01:19:32,594 --> 01:19:34,152
I'm not so sure.

1263
01:19:37,332 --> 01:19:38,458
Come and see us?

1264
01:19:38,533 --> 01:19:41,661
I can't promise.

1265
01:19:48,810 --> 01:19:50,004
He'll come, yeah.

1266
01:19:54,816 --> 01:19:56,113
Hello.

1267
01:19:57,486 --> 01:19:58,783
Thank you.

1268
